                                            ittf <div class="L1"><span class="pp-ln">   1 </span><span class="pp-pln"></span><span class="pp-kwd">└group</span></div><div class="L2"><span class="pp-ln">   2 </span><span class="pp-pln">    </span><span class="pp-tag">e</span><span class="pp-pln"> exportTo : schemaitem</span></div><div class="L3"><span class="pp-ln">   3 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> Require the emission, in the WizziModelType of the schema, of a function</span></div><div class="L4"><span class="pp-ln">   4 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> for exporting the model instance to a different format.</span></div><div class="L5"><span class="pp-ln">   5 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> There are a few built-in ExportTo functions. New export formats may be created</span></div><div class="L6"><span class="pp-ln">   6 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> by WizziPackage developers using methods.</span></div><div class="L7"><span class="pp-ln">   7 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">tag</span><span class="pp-pln"> export-to</span></div><div class="L8"><span class="pp-ln">   8 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">restrict</span></div><div class="L9"><span class="pp-ln">   9 </span><span class="pp-pln">            </span><span class="pp-tag">enum</span><span class="pp-pln"> json</span></div><div class="L0"><span class="pp-ln">  10 </span><span class="pp-pln">            </span><span class="pp-tag">enum</span><span class="pp-pln"> xml</span></div><div class="L1"><span class="pp-ln">  11 </span><span class="pp-pln">            </span><span class="pp-tag">enum</span><span class="pp-pln"> prettify</span></div><div class="L2"><span class="pp-ln">  12 </span><span class="pp-pln