re : schemaitem</span></div><div class="L4"><span class="pp-ln">  24 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> a section for top level (module scope) variable and functions declarations</span></div><div class="L5"><span class="pp-ln">  25 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">r</span><span class="pp-pln"> statement/s</span></div><div class="L6"><span class="pp-ln">  26 </span><span class="pp-pln">    </span><span class="pp-tag">e</span><span class="pp-pln"> method : schemaitem</span></div><div class="L7"><span class="pp-ln">  27 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> A method of an element pseudo-class generated in the WizziModelType.</span></div><div class="L8"><span class="pp-ln">  28 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">tag</span><span class="pp-pln"> m</span></div><div class="L9"><span class="pp-ln">  29 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">a</span><span class="pp-pln"> emitkey</span></div><div class="L0"><span class="pp-ln">  30 </span><span class="pp-pln">            </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> The emit key of the artifact which should insert this method.</span></div><div class="L1"><span class="pp-ln">  31 </span><span class="pp-pln">            </span><span class="pp-tag">#</span><span class="pp-pln"> Can be any string that artifact generators will filter.</span></div><div class="L2"><span class="pp-ln">  32 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">r</span><span class="pp-pln"> param/s</span></div><div class="L3"><span class="pp-ln">  33 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">r</span><span class="pp-pln"> require/s</span></div><div class="L4"><span class="pp-ln">  34 </span><span class="pp-pln">        </span><span class="pp-tag">r</span><span class="pp-pln"> statement/s</span></div><div class="L5"